<h3 id="install-gems">Install gems</h3>

<p>Run the following to install required gems defined in <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Gemfile</code>:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ bundle install
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="customization">Customization</h3>

<p>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_data/me.yml</code> to tweek the site configuration to your need. See corresponding fileâ€™s comments for details.</p>

<p>You also should replace the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/favicon.ico</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/assets/img/me.png</code> file with your own.</p>

<h3 id="run-locally">Run locally</h3>

<p>Run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">bundle exec serve --watch</code> to run it locally.</p>
